reviewText: The series was winding down at this point but still fun.
purchased for my mother who loves this series. I am very happy with the purchase. Seller description is exact; received product quicker than expected.
I enjoyed the dvds.  Watching this brings back memories.
This was a last minute xmas gift for my mother.  I was nervous that it wouldn't make it on time.  It was here just before xmas.
Great tv show and I can't wait to see more of them. I got my mom interested in the show alltogether

I am viewing Dark Shadows as an adult after having even an avid fan in my childhood. What can be better than this?  I love everything about it, including the live occasional gaffes. You will enjoy Angelique, Barnabas, parallel time, and the many plots and sub-plots. Watch the characters as they act out different roles in these episodes. Get out your cup of tea and have a marathon viewing!  I allow myself this little bit of fun every evening. It's a clean bit of fun in my day.
Great quality DVD, Everything as promised, fast delivery!
Only wish it had closed captioning.
Well packaged, great series. Angelique is the primary subject in the parallel time band.
